{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1679-01_247", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Autres [étrennes] données à Dijon]"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", janvier 1679 [tome 1], p.  247-252."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Ce n’est pas seulement à Paris que l’Amour inspire la libéralité. Il la fait régner dans les Provinces ; & les Etrennes qu’envoya un jeune Cavalier de Dijon à sa Maîtresse le premier jour de l’Année, vous feront connoistre que la galanterie est de tout Païs. Elles consistoient en une Agraffe, une Busquiere, & des Boucles de Souliers de Diamans. Tout cela estoit dans une Boëte, autour de laquelle on avoit peint les Chifres du Cavalier & de la Belle, en miniature. Ces Chifres estoient entrelacez ensemble, avec ces mots écrits en petites lettres d’or, qui servoient comme de bordure."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Quando còsi sarano î cûori ?"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Les Vers suivans estoient sous la Boëte."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Je ne puis regarder d’un oeil indiférent"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Mon Chifre avec celuy de la Belle que j’aime,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]/seg[1]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]/seg[1]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]/seg[2]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]/seg[2]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "N'y m’empescher de dire en soûpirant,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Helas ! quand verrons-nous nos cœurs unis de mesme ?"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[3]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Il y avoit une Devise sur la mesme Boëte, qui representoit un More adorant le Soleil ; ce qui faisoit allusion au nom & aux armes du Cavalier. L'ame de cette Devise estoit,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Adoro chi mi arde."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[4]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Sous la Devise, c’est à dire au fonds du couvercle de la Boëte, on lisoit ces Vers."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Je sens que j’aime, Iris ; mais pour pour bien l’exprimer,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[2]/seg[1]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[2]/seg[1]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[2]/seg[2]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[2]/seg[2]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "C'est trop peu que le mot d’"}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "aimer"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[2]/text()[2]", "text": "."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[5]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Dans la Boëte, au dessus des Pierreries, on trouva ces autres Vers."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[3]/seg[1]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[3]/seg[1]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[3]/seg[2]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[3]/seg[2]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[3]/seg[3]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[3]/seg[3]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Pour renouveller tous les ans"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[4]/seg[1]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[4]/seg[1]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[4]/seg[2]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[4]/seg[2]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[4]/seg[3]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[4]/seg[3]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Sa flâme, & ses empressemens,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[5]/seg[1]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[5]/seg[1]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[5]/seg[2]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[5]/seg[2]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Voicy le jour où chaque coeur étale"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Tout ce que peut l’Amour inspirer aux Amans ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais, belle Iris, pour vous, vous sçavez qu’en tout temps"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[8]/seg[1]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[8]/seg[1]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[8]/seg[2]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[8]/seg[2]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[8]/seg[3]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[8]/seg[3]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Ma tendresse est toûjours égale."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[6]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Les deux qui suivent estoient dans le papier qui envelopoit l’Agraffe de Diamans."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": "Encor que nostre éclat nous rende prêtieux,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[10]/text()[1]", "text": "Il cedera toûjours à celuy de vos yeux."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[7]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Le Billet qui estoit avec la Busquiere, contenoit ceux-cy."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[11]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[11]/seg[1]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[11]/seg[1]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[11]/seg[2]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[11]/seg[2]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[11]/text()[1]", "text": "Que nostre sort, belle Iris, sera doux !"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[12]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[12]/text()[1]", "text": "Et que nostre bonheur va faire de jaloux !"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[8]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Ces derniers se trouverent dans l’envelope des Boucles de Souliers. Ils faisoient parler les Diamans."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[13]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[13]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous n’avez pour charmer aucun besoin de nous ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[14]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[14]/seg[1]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[14]/seg[1]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[14]/seg[2]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[14]/seg[2]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[14]/seg[3]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[14]/seg[3]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[14]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais quoy que tout soit beau chez nous,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[15]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[15]/text()[1]", "text": "Et doive s’attirer conqueste sur conqueste."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[16]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[16]/seg[1]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[16]/seg[1]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[16]/seg[2]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[16]/seg[2]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[16]/seg[3]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[16]/seg[3]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[16]/text()[1]", "text": "Peut-estre qu’avec tant d’appas"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[17]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[17]/seg[1]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[17]/seg[1]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[17]/seg[2]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[17]/seg[2]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[17]/seg[3]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[17]/seg[3]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[17]/text()[1]", "text": "Sans nous vous ne brilleriez pas"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[18]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[18]/seg[1]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[18]/seg[1]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[18]/seg[2]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[18]/seg[2]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[18]/seg[3]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/l[18]/seg[3]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/l[18]/text()[1]", "text": "Depuis les pieds jusqu’à la teste."}]}]}